(10,2,2,28,'<div align=\"left\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Simsun; line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我的创业之路：一切只因结缘于七老<br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">题记：感谢有缘相识于七老，相遇奋斗于同一战线上的伙伴们，待我们强大，我们给自己天下。<br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">相识篇<br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">我是小淼儿。在接触到七老之前，小淼我是凑着微商的热闹在玩着销售衣服的，小白一个的我每天就知道找新款衣服上传空间，加加好友，聊聊客户，赚的还是可观的。<br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">直到有一天，不知道哪里来的就看空间里面有七老这个牌子的护肤品，其实我空间里卖护肤品的牌子太多了，只有七老引起了我的兴趣，理由很简单：其他牌子一样整天只刷产品图片毫无新意，谁知道效果好不好，我对此都是一概无视掉。唯独七老每天的客户反馈见证图和客户成交图让我很是好奇，更诱惑的是，她们好多七老的代理商竟然能够做到全职，更有甚者还专门辞职去做七老。呆在家里就能工作真是自由舒服呀，这下勾起了我 好奇心。天天受着七老的诱惑谁受得了，终于按捺不住，去寻问七老的产品和代理制度。<br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">如何加入七老的过程此处省略N个字。\r\n	</div>\r\n<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">但我只想说的一点就是我选择上家不是只一味地选择能力者，选择热情周到能为自己解决遇到的困难更为重要。（哈哈，这个也是我一直在努力做好的）。个人觉得无论做什么，只有自己的努力才能决定自己发展的长度和宽度。当然选择了就必须踏踏实实地认准了上家跟着干，上家其实就是伯乐，如果没有你的上家，可能你不会遇上七老，就得感恩她们带自己进入这个品牌行业。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">发展篇<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">自己买了产品适用（满<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">298<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">元就可以代理喽，没有其它任何代理费用滴），其实此时我还是对七老的产品的效果不是很了解的，必须自己用了才知道。拿回来用了清洁去油的赤芍洗面奶，感觉洗了之后脸好清爽干净；还有赤芍玉颜膜，涂得整个脸黑黑的还很舒服搞笑<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">……<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">彻底就给七老给征服了，哈哈，还拍照上传空间给秀了出来。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">入一行爱一行，我当时就把主做<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">QQ<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">号<span .=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">845051797</span>上的衣服全部下架，上传七老图片和日志，像是入魔一样整天抱着产品手册和手机研究着七老产品的有关资料。毫不犹豫，因为我相信七老能给我更好的未来。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">（好多人会说你就这样相信七老啦，未免太轻浮了吧？在这里要说下的是我不止是通过空间来了解七老的，也是有去当地的店里面考察药妆的，觉得现在大多数人有问题性皮肤，市场上针对祛斑祛痘的产品没有很多也不像七老这么齐全，这可是很有前景的呢。）<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">或许好多伙伴们会指望亲朋好友们来光顾七老，这个有当然是最好的呢。但我认为好产品总会有人懂得赏识的，走出去陌生人的市场才是巨大的。前期我能做的就是摆正好自己的心态，以真诚负责的态度去对等身边的人对七老的态度，因为总会有人对某一新鲜事物持反对或者不待见态度的（我们可以私下认为别人的不屑并不是真的不屑，只嫉妒的另一种表现）。当然钱在她们自己兜里，我们不强迫不强卖，以坦荡地心去宣传七老。爱美之心人皆有之，好的产品她们会看在眼里，需要地会自己来购买的，我们能做的就是发宣传提醒购买。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">做宣传的同时我觉得也要好好来包装一下自己，刚开始起来不要直接发产品使用对比图和其他客户购买成交图。我首先发些自己使用产品的图片和心得（这也是我后期对新加入的伙伴们常说的要多晒晒自己和产品的使用图片，赢得好友的信任），然后慢慢发表一些护肤知识和产品介绍图片和资料（把自己培养成一个真正有学习护肤知识的美容顾问），最后过一段时间我才会上传客户使用的对比截图和成交记录（哈哈，整个上手过程毫无违和感吧）。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">我相信很多伙伴们懂得傻逼一样的坚持，总会得到牛逼一样的结果！<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">初入微商行业，前两个月是积累提高自己营销知识和护肤知识期，坚持充实自己能力和扩大粉丝量才是首要的目标。不要只看到眼前的物质收获，真正的大伽都是经过深沉而后爆发出来的（切记不要涉足<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">365<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">行，因为没有哪个成功者是开着杂货店起家的），也庆幸自己没有在这个过程中迷失自己当初加入七老的心。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">当然前期有很多双眼睛在默默地注意着自己和产品，坚持下来让她们看到是真的可行，产品是真的科学。我的家人并不反对我做七老，还帮忙给别人介绍七老，帮我拉代理客户。妹妹也跟着我<a href=\"http://www.daxues.cn/forum-59-1.html%5C%22+target=%5C%22_blank%5C%22+.=%5C%22relatedlink%5C%22+.=%5C%22word-wrap:+break-word;+color:+rgb%2851,+102,+153%29;+border-bottom-width:+1px;+border-bottom-.:+solid;+border-bottom-color:+blue;\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#333333;text-decoration:none;\">兼职</a>做的，月收入也是可观的。我也暗自下决心要做好来，才能对得起他们对我的支持，现在我也做到能让家人满意的结果。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">卖产品前先卖自己，这个我觉得很好道理哦！除了好的产品，也需要好的人品和好形象。网络的虚拟化不利于客户直接了解我们，我会做好自己的<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">QQ<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">资料和空间相册，真实的分享自己的兴趣和生活，吸引志同道合的朋友，让好友信任自己。还要多做情感互动，关注好友的动态（点赞，评论，送礼等），一方面是给予好友的关注感，一方面是提醒你的存在。在这个过程中遇到能帮忙的事就尽量去拉一把，善良的付出总会得到感恩的回报。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">在做销售的过程中，或多或少会遇到成交失败的时候，不要灰心。因为有句话说别人的拒绝是销售的开始，同时也是信任建立的开始。可以这么理解，之所以会拒绝，是因为对产品产生了怀疑；之所以会怀疑，是因为对产品产生兴趣和关注了。我们得感到高兴，因为我们前两个月积累的过硬的产品和营销实力终于能有用武之地了。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">具体对付客户的拒绝我们可以用以下几个方法：反问法；以退为进法；优劣对比法；算账法；分析法；恐吓法，建<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">-<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">折<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">-<font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">建法等。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">感恩篇<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">相信很多人和我一样，在微商路上相识了很多交心知心的伙伴。无论线上线下，因为共同的目标携手共进。我们收获的不仅是金钱物质，更多的是一种彼此的相信感，自我价值的实现，梦想的成长。在此之前，我不懂具体的营销，没有团队，现在通过努力和幸运找到了生命中这么多有缘的小伙伴。每次听到你们说皮肤变好了，赚到钱了，团队新进伙伴了，生活充实了，营销学习进步了，我都是那么的开心。我们都是微商，做着让微商温暖微商的行动，从心底里感到了莫大的幸福。<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br .=\"word-wrap: break-word;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font face=\"宋体\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 7pt;\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">在此，我很感恩小伙伴们的信任。素未谋面的我们因为相信，所以信任。我会尽最大的能力做到互帮互助，永远相亲相爱，你若不离，我定不弃！总有人要赢的，为什么不能是我们，奋斗吧！<font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\" .=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font .=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-siz